      },
      "type": "event-comparison",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Below are some extremely popular samples that illustrate the prevalence of this riddim throughout the genre's development and global expansion. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "includes": [
        "media",
        "annotations",
